sequenceDiagram
  actor Student
  participant Web as React Web Client
  participant TutorApi as TutorController
  participant API as StudentProfileController
  participant Auth as AuthGuard
  participant Tutor as TutorService
  participant Profile as StudentProfileService
  participant Knowledge as KnowledgeService
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant AIModel as AiModelService
  participant Policy as AiOperationPolicyService
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI-backed model provider

  Student->>Web: Log in or register
  Web->>API: GET /student-profile/me
  API->>Auth: Validate session cookie
  Auth-->>API: Authenticated student
  API->>Profile: getStatus(user)
  Profile->>DB: Read student_profiles
  DB-->>Profile: No profile found
  API-->>Web: onboardingRequired=true
  Web-->>Student: Show voice-first meeting screen
  opt Page reload with unfinished meeting
    Web->>TutorApi: GET /tutor/lessons?scope=active&limit=4&turnLimit=8
    TutorApi->>Tutor: getLessonHistory(scope active)
    Tutor->>DB: Read active meeting lesson and recent turns
    Tutor-->>TutorApi: Active meeting history
    TutorApi-->>Web: Restore conversationId, lessonSessionId, and transcript
  end
  Student->>Web: Click green start voice meeting button
  Web->>TutorApi: POST /tutor/message lessonType=meeting
  TutorApi->>Auth: Validate session cookie
  Auth-->>TutorApi: Authenticated student
  TutorApi->>Tutor: Start AI-led meeting turn
  Tutor->>AIModel: Tutor meeting answer
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Create meeting response
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Short question or diagnostic prompt
  AIModel-->>Tutor: Meeting answer
  Tutor->>DB: Persist tutor_turns with lesson_type=meeting
  Tutor-->>TutorApi: Meeting answer and conversationId
  TutorApi-->>Web: Visible tutor answer
  Web-->>Student: Speak answer and reopen mic only while lifecycle is non-terminal
  Student->>Web: Reply by voice or text
  Web->>TutorApi: POST /tutor/message with same conversationId
  TutorApi->>Tutor: Continue meeting turn
  Tutor->>DB: Persist additional meeting turn
  Tutor-->>TutorApi: Meeting answer
  TutorApi-->>Web: Visible tutor answer
  Web->>API: GET /student-profile/me/meeting-readiness?conversationId
  API->>Profile: getMeetingReadiness(user, conversationId)
  Profile->>DB: Read meeting turns and active meeting lesson_session
  Profile-->>API: Readiness score, present signals, missing signals
  API-->>Web: Enable profile action only when backend says ready
  Student->>Web: Create profile from conversation
  Web->>API: POST /student-profile/me/from-conversation
  API->>Profile: completeOnboardingFromConversation(user, conversationId)
  Profile->>DB: Read stored meeting tutor_turns for user and conversation
  DB-->>Profile: Meeting transcript
  Profile->>Profile: Recheck readiness and required teaching signals
  Profile->>DB: Claim student_profile_creation_runs by user + conversation + transcript hash
  alt Duplicate completed run
    Profile->>DB: Read stored student_profiles
    Profile-->>API: Existing profile status
    API-->>Web: onboardingRequired=false and profile
  else New or retryable run
  Profile->>AIModel: Extract onboarding answers from transcript with lessonSessionId
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve onboardingConversationExtraction policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Extractor role, model, metadata, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Create extraction response
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Teaching-only onboarding answers
  AIModel-->>Profile: Extracted answer JSON
  Profile->>Knowledge: getActiveVectorStoreIds()
  Knowledge->>DB: Read env ids, project_ai_resources, or active knowledge_files
  Knowledge-->>Profile: Vector store ids
  Profile->>AIModel: Math knowledge diagnostician with conversationId and lessonSessionId
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve onboardingKnowledgeDiagnosis policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Specialist role, model, metadata, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Create specialist response
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: knowledgeState with evidence
  AIModel-->>Profile: knowledgeState
  Profile->>AIModel: Psychopedagogical profiler with lesson usage context
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve onboardingPsychopedagogicalProfile policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Specialist role, model, metadata, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Create specialist response
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: learningPreferences and psychologicalProfile
  AIModel-->>Profile: learningPreferences and safe profile hypotheses
  Profile->>AIModel: Teaching strategy planner with lesson usage context
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve onboardingStrategyPlan policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Specialist role, model, metadata, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Create specialist response
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: explanationStrategy and aiSummary
  AIModel-->>Profile: strategy and summary
  Profile->>DB: Upsert student_profiles
  Profile->>DB: Mark meeting lesson_session finished with goal reached
  Profile->>DB: Mark student_profile_creation_runs completed
  Profile-->>API: Profile status
  API-->>Web: onboardingRequired=false and profile
  Web-->>Student: Open tutor workspace with lesson launcher
  end
